high_descs: Turn right, exit at the end, cross to the right. Straight to the door. Cross to the right. Exit. Turn left. Cross to the right and then to the left, in front of the fridge.
Open the refrigerator. Take the knife. Close the refrigerator.
Turn to the left. Move over. Cross to the right. Reach the bottom. Cross to the left. Enter the room. Cross to the right and then to the left. Stand in front of the pan shelf.
Open the shelf, place the knife at the bottom of the pan.
Remove the pan with the knife. Close the door of the shelf.
Exit the room. Turn right. Go straight ahead, cross to the right after the refrigerator. Continue until you have the countertop. Turn left.
Place the pan and knife on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Find a Knife, a Pan and place them on the CounterTop.

high_descs: Head to the bedroom exit at the right and turn left to enter the kitchen and face the fridge.
Take out the knife from the fridge.
Walk down the passage on the left and head to the closet room on the left to reach the pan in the cupboard on the left.
Put the knife in the pan on the bottom of the shelf.
Take out the pan from the cupboard.
Turn around to exit the room and turn right to walk down the passage and turn left to reach the kitchen countertop on the left.
Put the pan on the countertop in between the two wooden boards.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife on the countertop with the pan.

high_descs: Turn right and turn left to the fridge.
Pick the knife from the fridge.
Turn left to the cabinet inside the pan.
Place the knife on the pan.
Pick the pan out from the cabinet.
Turn left and turn left to the countertop.
Place the pan on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place the pan on the countertop.
